node.text:
💀Spooky season approaches! Get cosy in a SKELETON HOUSE SWEATER!💀

We visited a cute forest to take these photos and the weather was beautiful...which we admit isn't that spooky. But that's okay! The sweater helps bring all of the spooky vibes 👻

We sold out of our first print run but a second print run is on the way and will start shipping at the start of October! Thank you to everyone who bought one so far, we can't wait to see a whole bunch of spooky sweater wearers!

(The sweaters were screenprinted by @blackwaterstudios and they look so nice!)

#halloween #spooky #skeletons #halloweensweater #sarahgraley #spookyart #screenprinting

node.text:
I mean, Stef can fight off the monster! Or at least give me a head start!

This throwback is from Our Super Adventure Vol. 3 - CUTE! 

Heya! Thank you so much to everyone who's ordered some spooky merch! Our first order of Skeleton House sweaters has now arrived so some orders will start to ship out this week! We're expecting a pin badge delivery super soon as well! 

We've now placed our order for Pumpkin Patch sweaters too - we've ordered a few extra in each size so if you missed out on the timed pre-order you've still got time!

We've also ordered more Skeleton House sweaters - the 2nd wave ones will ship at the start of October with the Pumpkin Patch sweaters! Phew!

Stay spooky y'all! 🦇

#comics #webcomic #wholesome #instacomic #igcomic #comicstrip #sarahgraley #oursuperadventure

node.text:
A special double length comic about Wilson and his fave new cushion! Swipe to the end to see a photo of the boy himself! 😼

Heya! I've got two spooky sweaters available to preorder right now! One is a brand new design called Skeleton House, and the other is a reprint of Pumpkin Patch - that last one is a timed preorder that ends THIS WEDNESDAY so get your order in now to make sure you get your size!

There's other spooky bits too! Go have a look and get spooky! It's never too early for spooky season! 💀🎃💀🎃💀

#comics #webcomic #instacomic #comicstrip #igcomic #sarahgraley #oursuperadventure #comic

node.text:
🎃🎃🎃 Spooky season approaches! 🎃🎃🎃

I'm launching a whole bunch of new spooky pins and a brand new spooky sweater on Wednesday! I'm so excited to share the new designs with you all!

I'm also opening up a week long pre-order for pumpkin patch sweaters on Wednesday too - we had a bunch of people get in touch asking us to restock it so make sure you set an alarm if you want one!

Lastly, my portrait commissions will open up again on Wednesday! I'll be taking on a limited amount of commissions for September so get in early if you want one! I've had so much fun drawing everyone and their pets!

#comics #webcomic #igcomics #comicstrip #instacomic #wholesome #spooky #halloween #sarahgraley #oursuperadventure
